        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:385:1",
        "relations": null,
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/207/255",
        "text": [
          "٢٠٧. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): إِنْ لَمْ تَكُنْ حَلِيماً فَتَحَلَّمْ، فَإِنَّهُ قَلَّ مَنْ تَشَبَّهَ بَقَوْمٍ إِلَّا أَوْشَكَ أَنْ يَكُونَ مِنْهُمْ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "207. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: If you cannot forbear, feign to do so because it is seldom that a man likens himself to a group and does not become as one of them. [1]"
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
